just thought of something, maybe add a test to AlterRegionCommandTest to make sure this converter is used. One of the effect of the converter is to make sure region name starts with a "/". Something like this:

  @Test
  public void regionNameIsConverted() {
    String command = "alter region --name=Person";
    GfshParseResult result = parser.parse(command);
    assertThat(result.getParamValue("name")).isEqualTo("/Person");
  }
